description:
Brooke and Danielle are talking all about their current favorite beauty products!  From haircare, to skincare and makeup, tune in to hear what the gals are loving right now.  Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies and stories!


SHOP GOTG MERCH! NEW DROP 4/28 at 1PM EST https://fanjoy.co/collections/gals-on-the-go  


Danielle’s Favorites!

SKIN
Sunday Riley CEO Glow
Caudalie Beauty Elixir
Tan Luxe Self Tan Drops 
Isle of Paradise Pro Glow Spray Tan Mister

MAKEUP
Kosas Revealer Concealer
Rare Beauty Liquid Luminizer in Outshine
Undone beauty blush 325 flare lip to cheek 
Chanel crème Les beiges bronzer
Makeup forever HD foundation 
Pat McGrath Lip Liner in Structure
Summer Fridays vanilla beige lip butter balm

glow recipe watermelon niacinamide dew drops
farmacy clearly clean cleansing balm
supergoop unseen suncreen
paulas choice 2% bha liquid exfoliant
summer fridays undereye cream

MAKEUP

item beauty blush

milk makeup bionic glow 


HAIR
